description: The video shows a black and white nighttime surveillance footage of a street. The camera is pointed at the street, which has two white lane markers in the center. The street is empty for most of the video except for the time when a vehicle drives by at 0:01. The vehicle has its headlights on and its headlights are visible as it drives by. The vehicle is too far away to make out its make or model. On the left side of the street there is a chain-link fence, a sidewalk, and a structure with corrugated metal roofing. There is also a metal pole with what looks like electrical wires running across the top. There is a date and time stamp on the video showing the date as 2024-05-28 and the time as 20:15:07.

The video is a black and white recording from a security camera.  The camera is pointed at a house with a bush in front of it.  It appears to be night time as the image is very dark and you can see light coming from a lamp on the porch.  The bushes move slightly as if there is wind and then a loud "beep beep beep" noise is heard.

The video is a surveillance camera recording taken in front of a house on a street. The house is on the left side of the video, and there are two trash cans next to the sidewalk in front of the house. There is a white car parked in front of the house. On the right side of the video, a black car is visible pulling into the driveway. A black SUV is also parked in the driveway. There are some houses in the background. The street is a cul-de-sac, and there is a light colored car driving in a circle and exiting out of frame. The date and time are displayed in the top left corner of the video. Just as the light colored car is turning to exit the cul-de-sac, a loud "P" sound can be heard.

The video is black and white footage of a car driving down a street at night. The camera is pointed at the street and the car is driving from the left to the right of the frame. It is a two-lane street with a white line separating the lanes. There is a fence and a street light on the left side of the road. The car has its headlights on and it is driving slowly. The date and time are displayed in the top left corner of the frame. The sound of the car driving and the wind blowing can be heard.

The video is in black and white and appears to be from a security camera. A truck is parked under a roof overhang, backing up towards the camera. It is in a gated driveway and there is a small window in the wall to the right of the truck. The time is 03:15:35 on 2024-05-28. A noise can be heard at about 0:28.

The video shows a living room with a family watching TV. The room is messy, with items scattered around. The camera is mounted high on the wall. The family is talking, but it is difficult to make out what they are saying. One person is asking if the door is open and another is talking about a sink. There are also two dogs in the room, one lying on the floor and the other lying on the couch.

The video is from a security camera and shows the front yard of a home. The camera is positioned under the carport of the home and is angled downward towards the street. The video starts with a red motorcycle and its rider driving past the camera and into the street. A boy in a yellow shirt then walks past the camera and towards the motorcycle. The boy and the motorcycle rider then walk into the street and out of view. The camera is stationary and does not move throughout the video. The timestamp on the video is 2024-05-28 17:09:10.

The video shows two brown dogs playing in a backyard. One dog is lying down, while the other dog is standing up and sniffing the ground. There is a yellow plastic crate in the foreground, a white toilet in the middle, and a blue bicycle and an old couch in the background. The video was recorded on May 26, 2024 at 6:46:05 PM.  The dogs appear to be enjoying themselves and playing with each other.

The video shows a living room with a woman sitting in a recliner with a dog at her feet. The woman is talking to someone off camera. There is a television on the wall and a fireplace on the floor, both of which are off.  The floor is covered with a lot of clutter and there are many items lying around on the coffee table in front of the woman. The woman is wearing light-colored pants and a white shirt. The dog is white and fluffy. The woman says, "You gonna hear about Dusty and a rabbit cooking". The camera pans to the right, and a young girl walks through a doorway in the background of the room. The woman says "Hey Sally how's your going over there". The girl doesn't respond. The woman says, "I'm working in there. I was just earning the money to spend in my college or whatever we are going to do.  I have the things thank you! Okay? Don't leave your door open". The girl is out of view behind the door. The woman continues, "I can't leave her door open"  The camera pans back to the woman and the dog. The woman's words suggest that she is talking to her daughter Sally about her plans for college. The woman is likely trying to motivate Sally to work hard so that she can pay for college, but Sally is not interested in talking to her mother.

The video is black and white. The camera is pointed at a man in a white t-shirt and white shorts. He is sitting in a leather recliner. He has tattoos on his arms. In front of him is a small table with several objects on it. The time is 2024-05-28 15:09:31. Two glowing, oval-shaped objects, one with the number "3" and the other with the number "5", are hanging from the ceiling. The man is looking at his phone. He seems to be scrolling through something on his phone.  The man does not move for the entire 25 seconds of the video. The only audio heard in the video is a monotone, female voice repeatedly saying numbers.

The video shows a view from a front porch looking out at a street and a grassy yard. The camera is mounted on the porch railing and there are vertical wooden railing slats in front of the camera lens. The sun is shining brightly, making it hard to see beyond the railings. A water bottle is sitting on top of the railing in the upper right corner of the frame. There is a house visible in the distance across the street and trees are visible in the background on the right side of the frame. A small tree is growing in the front yard and a large, light-colored trash can is just to the left of the small tree.  There is a bird perched on a wire above the trash can that makes a "peep" sound as it flutters its wings.  The date and time stamp, 2024-05-27 20:40:29, is visible in the upper left corner of the frame.

The video is a black and white night vision recording of a large window with multiple panes. The camera is pointing upwards and slightly to the left, so the frame is mostly taken up by the window. It appears to be an exterior shot of a home. There is some movement inside the home, which is visible through the window, but the footage is too dark to make out any details. The sounds in the video are of a soft breeze rustling leaves, the chirping of crickets, and the occasional distant bark of a dog. There is a faint, high-pitched noise that starts at about 0:29. It is a rhythmic "p" sound, like someone is repeatedly saying the letter "p" while breathing out.  It seems to be coming from the direction of the window. It is unclear if the strange sound is coming from the interior of the house or from an animal outside. The video is 30 seconds long.

The video shows a backyard scene. A security camera is mounted on the side of a mobile home, pointing toward a wooden structure and a grassy area. A red minivan is parked behind the structure, and a basketball hoop is visible in the distance. The lawn is covered in clover. There are several pieces of furniture and other items scattered around the yard, including a kid-sized go-kart, several chairs, and a table. The camera picks up the sound of birds chirping. The video is shaky and blurry.

The video is a close-up shot of a security camera inside a shop. It appears to be a party supply store. The camera is positioned at counter level, with various party supplies, including streamers, plastic cups, and confetti visible in the background. The camera captures a loud, high-pitched noise beginning at the start of the video and lasting throughout the clip. The source of the noise is not identifiable, however, the sound is clearly emanating from somewhere within the store.

The video is a black and white night vision recording from a security camera. It is set in a kitchen. The camera is pointed at a living room that is connected to the kitchen. The living room is dimly lit and contains an armchair, an end table with a lamp and a framed picture on it, and another table with an unrecognizable object on it. The living room walls are covered in pictures and decorations. The camera is positioned on a counter near a sink. There is a ceiling fan in the background of the living room.  There is a brief, high-pitched sound that begins around 0:30 seconds.  It's unclear what the video shows or what the high-pitched sound is.

The video is black and white and appears to be from a security camera. It shows a dark figure moving in a backyard. There are some items in the backyard, including a small table and a lawn mower. The figure appears to be moving around the table. There are a few bushes and trees visible in the background. The figure’s movements are somewhat erratic and the figure's identity is unclear. The person filming or the people in the video are making some kind of noise in the background.

The video is a grainy black and white recording from a security camera. The camera is mounted on the side of a house facing a deck and yard. There is a man sitting on the deck looking down. There is a small wooden structure next to him, as well as a table and chairs to his right. The grass and bushes are visible in the background, and a basketball hoop can be seen further back. A dark colored SUV is parked in the driveway with its headlights on.  Several rustling noises are heard throughout the video.

The video is a still shot from a security camera. The camera is pointed towards a front porch with a wooden railing. Through the railing and glass door, we can see a driveway with a silver minivan parked on the left side.  There is a house in the background with a pink or red brick exterior. Behind the house is a green, leafy forest. There is a water bottle sitting on the top of the railing.  On the right side, we can see more trees, some of which are slightly swaying in the breeze. The date and time stamp is visible in the upper left-hand corner of the frame. There is a faint whistling sound, but it is not clear what is making the noise.

The video shows a black and white image of a room with a small sofa in the center of the frame, and a water cooler on the left side of the frame. There is a light switch on the right wall. The date and time is displayed in the top left corner. The video lasts for 18 seconds, and there is no audio. A low-pitched, extended "p" sound starts at 00:18, making it clear that there is likely audio that has been muted.

The video shows a still shot of a small wooden cabin with a brick facade. There are two doors and a few windows on the front of the cabin. There is a wooden deck on the front of the cabin, and a red brick path leading up to the front door. There are two thatched-roof umbrellas in front of the cabin, one with a bench and the other with a table and chairs. To the right of the path, there is a large blue inflatable pool. There are trees and bushes in the background. The date and time are shown in the top left corner of the screen.  The video is blurry, and the audio is faint and unintelligible.
